version_description:
ios 10 bug fixes.
Greatly reduced app size.

Fixed iOS10 bug where transferred files could not be opened.
Open files from other apps.

New Logo!
Improved UI.
We now show file transfer speeds.
More awesomeness.
We've added Feem WebShare. Now you can share files without Feem installed on the other device.

- Compatible with iPhone X.
- Integration with iOS 11 Files App.
- Bug Fix: Transfer .HEIC photos.
- Bug Fix: import multiple audio files.

Bug fix for failed picture transfers on iOS13.
No more wait times when selecting recent photos and videos to send.
Added location permission, which is required to display the name of your Wi-Fi network.
Select files to send from iOS's Files.app.
Bug fix: Crash when loading photos
